-1212855682.text: "33 To determine whether the cells showing phosphorylation of Aurora B also showed phosphorylation of histone H3, CHK1 depleted HCT116 p53-/- cells treated with thymidine for 24h were fixed and stained for pSer10-histone H3 and pThr232 Aurora B content using mouse anti-pSer10 histone H3 and rabbit anti-phospho Aurora kinase antibodies."
